These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
Pet: bird, ferret, hedgehog, mouse
1. Pet:bird is on the right of Pet:mouse##1
2. Pet:ferret is somewhere between Pet:hedgehog and Pet:mouse##7
3. Pet:hedgehog is on the left of Pet:ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | hedgehog | ferret | mouse | bird |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
