2. Food:banana is somewhere between Food:pineapple and Food:onion##7
3. Food:banana is between Food:pineapple and Food:grapes##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | onion | grapes | banana | pineapple |

