.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
Movie-Genre: scientific, satire, romance, musical
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the right of Movie-Genre:satire##1
2. Movie-Genre:satire is between Movie-Genre:scientific and Movie-Genre:musical##2
3. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:romance##3
4. Movie-Genre:scientific is somewhere between Movie-Genre:romance and Movie-Genre:musical##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | scientific | satire | musical |

